commitmsg:
Merge pull request #2 from dlo/patch-1

Remove duplicated lines

Revert "Enforce valid captcha only if required, so tests can relax captcha requirement"

This reverts commit c3c450b1a7070a1dd1b808e55371e838dd297857. It wasn't
such a great idea.
Enforce valid captcha only if required, so tests can relax captcha requirement
Removed error dict from field class.
What was I smoking when I wrote that last sentence?
Added information about new RECAPTCHA_USE_SSL setting.
Updated README to note requirement for custom python-recaptcha library at: http://github.com/bltravis/python-recaptcha

Moved captcha validation out of field clean() method and into form clean(), and added an extra field (remote_ip) to the RegistrationFormCaptcha form class to allow setting of remote_ip value via a custom register view in views.py. Also added settings hooks and tests to ReCaptcha widget to properly utilize SSL when required.
